ZH: 戒骄戒躁，不可沉溺于虚荣。
EN: Be humble and patient, do not indulge in vanity.

ZH: 戒骄戒躁，要脚踏实地努力工作。
EN: Stay humble and patient, work hard with your feet on the ground.

